DuckChat2
=========
DuckChat supporting distributed servers.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Prerequisits
- User must be on a SunOS system or a Linux machine.
    + Verify this by running command 'uname' and make sure it matches to either
    of the two strings "SunOS" or "Linux"
- POSIX Sockets library

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Building DuckChat2

To build the binaries, simply run 'make' from the project directory. The
resulting server and client binary will be placed in the bin/ directory. 
